I would prefer this to be mocked instead of creating a new instance.
Something like:
def createInvalidJson() {
        def multipartFile = Mock(MockMultipartFile)
        multipartFile.name >> 'jsonFile'
        multipartFile.getBytes() >> { throw new IOException("Error reading JSON file") }
        multipartFile.getInputStream() >> { throw new IOException("Error reading JSON file") }
        return multipartFile
    }
